additionalProperty.name: Ingredients
additionalProperty.value: INGREDIENTS: Lamington Sponge [Wheat Flour, Sugar, Water, Egg Powder, Emulsifiers ((471, 475, 481 from Palm**), 322 (Soy)), Raising Agents (450, Sodium Carbonate, 341), Humectants (420, 1520), Starches (Wheat, Tapioca, Maize), Thickeners (1422, 1442), Salt, Preservatives (Sorbic Acid, Potassium Sorbate)], Lamington Dip [Sugar, Water, Cocoa Powder (5%), Canola Oil, Natural Flavourings, Thickeners (412, 415, 406), Preservative (Potassium Sorbate)], Jam Filling (15%) [Sugar, Apple, Gelling Agent (440), Acidity Regulator (330), Natural Colour (163), Natural Raspberry Flavour, Preservative (Potassium Sorbate)], Desiccated Coconut (6.5%) [Coconut, Preservative (223)].
